don't you think it'll be more humiliating?

583
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:13,920
Whoever is the leading actor

584
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,360
will be responsible for the rating.

585
00:21:16,120 --> 00:21:18,760
