If the rating is good,

587
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:22,080
Chun Lei will be the one who deserves credit.

588
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:23,360
If the rating is bad,

589
00:21:23,360 --> 00:21:25,120
Peng will be the target of criticism.

590
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:27,000
What will you lose?

591
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,240
Did you study accounting?

592
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,960
You certainly did some calculations.

593
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,360
I just have a thick skin.

594
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,040
If I have offended you already, then I'll just continue.

595
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,080
If I were Chun Lei,

596
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:38,880
I would not only play this role,

597
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,640
but also

598
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:42,000
help Peng with his acting

599
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,760
if I have time and energy.

600
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:46,280
We would work together
to present a good show to the audience.

601
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:48,080
Then, the producer,

602
00:21:48,080 --> 00:21:48,760
the director,

603
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:50,080
and Peng,

604
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:50,880
would all

605
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:53,760
speak highly of Chun Lei.

606
00:21:53,760 --> 00:21:55,160
The respect that Chun Lei earns this way

607
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:57,880
would be much more
than his name being on top of the credits.

608
00:21:57,880 --> 00:21:59,440
Only when the experienced help the young

609
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:01,640
will this industry have a future.

610
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,480
What do you think, Ms. Hua?

611
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,240
As I said,

612
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:11,200
this is not Chun Lei's choice.

613
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,320
It's mine.

614
00:22:12,320 --> 00:22:14,240
If you think we're petty,

615
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:15,640
then it's me,

616
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:17,040
not Chun Lei.

617
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:18,440
No, Ms. Hua.

618
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:19,600
As soon as you came in,

619
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:21,960
I've been listening to you talking.

620
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:23,760
You are clear-minded

621
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:26,280
and cool-headed.

622
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:28,240
You treat the talents as your own family.

623
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,920
You let them take all the glamour,

624
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,560
while you put up with all the trouble.

625
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:32,920
Across the industry,

626
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,080
everyone doesn't call you Big Sister

627
00:22:34,080 --> 00:22:35,120
for nothing.

628
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:36,480
What's your name again?

629
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:37,720
Dai Xiaoyu.

630
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:41,200
Dai Xiaoyu, listen.

631
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:44,040
No one dares to speak of Chun Lei like this

632
00:22:44,040 --> 00:22:45,440
in front of me.

633
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:47,640
You

634
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,400
gave me all the harsh words

635
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:51,480
and then made up with all the compliments.

636
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:52,880
You acted like you were so genuine

637
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:53,640
and straightforward.

638
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,920
You slapped me and then gave me some sugar.

639
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,240
You pretended to be joking but you actually meant it.

640
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,520
In fact,

641
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,480
it was just a desperate move.

642
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:02,240
You took a leap of faith.

643
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,760
Am I right?

644
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,280
Excuse me, Ms. Hua.

645
00:23:05,280 --> 00:23:06,920
I just think that...

646
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:09,000
Don't tell me what you think.

647
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:12,200
I only care what I think.

648
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,680
I think

649
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:16,760
you're right.

650
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:21,160
Your words were harsh.

651
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,680
But I heard every one of it.

652
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:25,280
Do you know what moved me most?

653
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:29,560
You said

654
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:33,120
that only when the experienced help the young

655
00:23:33,120 --> 00:23:35,040
will the industry have a future.

656
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,560
Even though you're young,

657
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:38,400
you are capable of saying something like this.

658
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,560
I have confidence in you.

659
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:41,080
Come on, pour me some wine.

660
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:43,080
Cheers, Ms. Hua.

661
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,640
Actually, you are not moved

662
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:49,160
by that sentence I said.

663
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:49,960
I know

664
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:52,440
you're weighing the pros and cons for Chun Lei.

665
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,720
Where did you find this clever one?

666
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,280
Ms. Hua, it's all fate.

667
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,680
Really, it's just fate.

668
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:03,080
Whether it was Chun Lei's decision

669
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,440
or mine,

670
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,520
from now on,

671
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,760
it's water under the bridge.

672
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:07,360
Mr. Chai,

673
00:24:07,360 --> 00:24:10,120
ask the producer to send me the contract

674
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:11,720
tomorrow.

675
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,320
Initiate the law approval process.

676
00:24:13,320 --> 00:24:14,840
We need more wine, Ms. Hua.

677
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,320
Use this cup.

678
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:19,800
Here, Xiaoyu.

679
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:20,320
Come on.

680
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:21,680
Thank you.

681
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:22,480
No problem.

682
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:23,360
Here you are.

683
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,640
Mr. Chai,

684
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,640
you don't need to

685
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:29,040
envy me for having so many talents.

686
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:31,080
You have Xiaoyu and that's enough.

687
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:31,640
Listen to me.

688
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,600
Treat her well.

689
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:34,400
Or I'll steal her from your company.

690
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:34,840
Of course.

691
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,480
I certainly will treat her well.

692
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:41,920
You said that your cousin

693
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,520
is an actress?

694
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,360
Yes.

695
00:24:44,360 --> 00:24:46,120
She's not a star, just a random actress.

696
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,960
Let me add you on WeChat.

697
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:49,280
You may introduce her

698
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,120
to me someday.

699
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:51,920
Sure.

700
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:53,800
I won't brag about other things.

701
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:54,840
But in terms of acting,

702
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:56,400
I can tell immediately

703
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,080
if someone has the gift.

704
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,480
That's great.

705
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,640
Ms. Hua agreed.

706
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:04,680
I told you that you can trust me.

707
00:25:05,360 --> 00:25:07,360
You're bragging already.

708
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:08,320
Listen,

709
00:25:08,360 --> 00:25:09,600
I agreed because I had some wine.

710
00:25:09,600 --> 00:25:11,000
I may break my word tomorrow.

711
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:12,440
You won't.

712
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:25,000
Mr. Chai, what is this...

713
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,280
Dai Xiaoyu.

714
00:25:27,280 --> 00:25:28,280
Tonight,

715
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:30,240
you made a great contribution.

716
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:31,640
This is your reward.

717
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:33,600
But this is too much.

718
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:36,040
Do you know how much we will make with this contract?

719
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,600
So it's only 1% of it.

720
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:40,440
Very appropriate.

721
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:42,040
Fine.

722
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,520
Then I'll take it.

723
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:44,560
Besides,

724
00:25:44,560 --> 00:25:46,280
you really blew my mind this evening.

725
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,720
You put Ms. Hua

726
00:25:48,360 --> 00:25:49,760
on a pedestal,

727
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:52,760
and then she couldn't get down.

728
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:54,960
I really didn't plan it.

729
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:56,520
You can't plan it.

730
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:59,400
It would be counterproductive.

731
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,240
Dai Xiaoyu, do you know

732
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,920
that you have three advantages

733
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:05,800
and you only used two of them?

734
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:08,000
First,

735
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,400
you're smart.

736
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:10,000
Second,

737
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:11,160
you can drink.

738
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,400
One bottle of wine

739
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:15,560
and you were on the right path to convince Ms. Hua.

740
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,480
Third,

741
00:26:17,760 --> 00:26:19,000
you're pretty.

742
00:26:19,840 --> 00:26:20,840
But with Ms. Hua,

743
00:26:20,840 --> 00:26:23,200
you haven't got a chance to use it.

744
00:26:23,560 --> 00:26:25,160
Once you make full use

745
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,520
of all your advantages,

746
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,720
you'll be unbeatable.

747
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:32,320
Dai Xiaoyu

748
00:26:32,320 --> 00:26:33,760
will become

749
00:26:33,760 --> 00:26:35,000
an indispensable figure

750
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:37,520
of our company.

751
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:40,040
Thanks for your advice, Mr. Chai.

752
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:41,160
Work hard.

753
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,280
Fighting!

754
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,440
I'm back.

755
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,600
Dad.

756
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:56,480
Where's your mother?

757
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:58,960
She's in a shower.

758
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,800
So you seized the chance to watch TV, right?

759
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:02,520
Right.

760
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:03,440
What are you watching?

761
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,960
The Dynasty of Sword.

762
00:27:05,320 --> 00:27:06,360
Wow, an action movie.

763
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:08,560
You're early today.

764
00:27:09,040 --> 00:27:10,480
I came back as soon as we finished.

765
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,600
How much did you drink today?

766
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:12,800
Just a bit.

767
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:14,000
You know Wu.

768
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,400
He wouldn't let anyone stay sober.

769
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:18,240
My son,

770
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,600
how's your homework going?

771
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:21,480
I've finished the math homework.

772
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:22,240
As to the composition...

773
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,000
I don't know how to write it.

774
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:24,480
You don't know how?

775
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,120
Ask your mother.

776
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,600
She can help you with it.

777
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:28,840
It's easy for you to give orders.

778
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:30,640
Daddy loves to give orders.

779
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,920
You majored in liberal arts.

780
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:34,360
You must be good at writing, right?

781
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,760
So you science students

782
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:37,040
are good at drinking?

783
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:37,520
Please.

784
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:39,440
It isn't that I love drinking or something.

785
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:41,560
If you don't love it, no one can force you.

786
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:45,320
It's just work and life.

787
00:27:46,760 --> 00:27:48,960
You surely know how to sublimate yourself.

788
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,760
What else can I do?

789
00:27:50,760 --> 00:27:53,600
Drinking is part of my job.

790
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:56,000
If I don't make money,

791
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:59,000
how can you live like this?

792
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,040
Live like what?

793
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,680
Look at me.

794
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:04,080
Do I look like my life is easy?

795
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:06,920
Come closer.

796
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,760
You're the mother of two kids.

797
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:13,240
Why are you still so beautiful?

798
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:17,640
Don't you get clever with me!

799
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:20,160
Have some mercy, please.

800
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,040
During the day,

801
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:22,080
I sit at my desk.

802
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:23,560
In the evening, I sit at the dinner table.

803
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:26,240
I almost got piles.

804
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,520
What's the subject of your composition?

805
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:29,640
"My Dad".

806
00:28:30,320 --> 00:28:32,080
Isn't this a piece of cake?

807
00:28:32,080 --> 00:28:33,080
You can just write

808
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:35,000
that your dad's name is Du Shijun.

809
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:36,560
During the day, he goes to work

810
00:28:36,560 --> 00:28:37,600
and I go to school.

811
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:39,040
In the evening, he comes back from work

812
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:40,240
drunk

813
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:41,840
and sleepy.

814
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:43,080
I don't know how he thinks of me

815
00:28:43,080 --> 00:28:44,560
and I don't know how I should think of him.

816
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:45,440
Hey, lady.

817
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:47,000
Who teaches one's son like that?

818
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,320
Please, tell me how you would do it.

819
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:52,880
Don't push me.

820
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:57,760
Zhuang.

821
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:00,120
Grab your notebook.

822
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:00,760
Come here.

823
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:02,400
Go. You can do it.

824
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:05,560
Have you finished?

825
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:06,760
OK, let's brush your teeth and go to bed.

826
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,920
It's just a composition.

827
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,320
Here.

828
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:17,080
Come here.

829
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:18,920
Here you are.

830
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:19,920
OK, I'll take it.

831
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,800
I don't want to eat it.

832
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:23,080
Fine, give it to me.

833
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:26,240
"My Dad".

834
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,520
Who is your dad?

835
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:29,760
Du Shijun.

836
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:32,160
What does he do?

837
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:33,800
He's an accountant.

838
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,960
Does your dad treat you well?

839
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:38,160
He treats me...

840
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,240
Yes, he treats me well.

841
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,200
Does your dad treat your mom well?

842
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,160
Not bad.

843
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:45,240
Who's the breadwinner

844
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,200
of the family?

845
00:30:15,520 --> 00:30:16,200
Mom,

846
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:18,280
my dad fell asleep.

847
00:30:18,280 --> 00:30:19,320
The composition is due on Monday.

848
00:30:19,320 --> 00:30:21,000
I don't want to do it anymore today.

849
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,240
Then you don't have to do it.

850
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,680
Just go to bed.

851
00:30:23,960 --> 00:30:25,200
I can close the door by myself.

852
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:26,800
Go right to sleep, alright?

853
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:41,840
You fell asleep?

854
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,240
No, I'm watching him.

855
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:45,040
You are watching him in your dreams.

856
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:46,840
Come on. Take a shower and go to sleep.

857
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:47,720
Where is he?

858
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:48,960
What are you talking about?

859
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:49,440
But...

860
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,240
Why did I think you could help with the homework?

861
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:53,680
I just rested my eyes for a bit.

862
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:54,720
You must be kidding me.

863
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,960
Where is he?

864
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:58,480
I already helped him set up the structure.

865
00:30:58,480 --> 00:30:59,560
Be quiet.

866
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,360
Take your shower.

867
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:53,760
It's midnight. When are you going to bed?

868
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:57,280
